name: Penis_Shadow_Realistic
description:
All examples use Realvision1.2

I'm not super happy with this. I tried to train different versions, but this one is the best I've managed. Weird blobs appear on the breasts some times. I don't know how to fix it. The face shapes are pretty much all the same. A lot of pointy chins. Lowering the weights too much makes the shadow less defined. If you're able to figure out a good prompt, please share.
